the host of heaven in the two courts of the house of the LORD.","year":-698},{"id":"recP8iP58Hvsoorae","ref":"2Kgs.21.6","text":"And he made his son pass through the fire, and observed times, and used enchantments, and dealt with familiar spirits and wizards: he wrought much wickedness in the sight of the LORD, to provoke him to anger.","year":-683},{"id":"recfaGUEnmymvDQvb","ref":"2Kgs.21.7","text":"And he set a graven image of the grove that he had made in the house, of which the LORD said to David, and to Solomon his son, In this house, and in Jerusalem, which I have chosen out of all tribes of Israel, will I put my name for ever:","year":-698},{"id":"recUSqisk20EVF6UE","ref":"2Kgs.21.8","text":"Neither will I make the feet of Israel move any more out of the land which I gave their fathers; only if they will observe to do according to all that I have commanded them, and according to all the law that my servant Moses commanded them.","year":-698}]}
